The Spiritline: Pom team will be testing a mobile app for the remainder of the school year. This is a beta app still in development, but can be used for team communications.

In order to get you set up with the app, Aktivate will be emailing you the credentials, links and instructions to download the app and login.

In order to get you set up with the app, Aktivate has emailed you the credentials, links, and instructions to download the app and log in. As a reminder, Aktivate acquired RegisterMyAthlete, so they have the email address you used to register at the start of the season. You should see an email from the Aktivate team in your inbox (check spam or junk filter)

Further team updates and summer plans will be sent out soon.

Thanks,
Coach Heytens

In order to get you set up with the app, Aktivate has emailed you the credentials, links, and instructions to download the app and log in. As a reminder, Aktivate acquired RegisterMyAthlete, so they have the email address you used to register at the start of the season. You should see an email from the Aktivate team in your inbox (check spam or junk filter)

Further team updates and summer plans will be sent out soon.

Thanks,
Coach Heytens

This would be connected to and eventually replace registermyathlete.
The goal is to make an all-in-one app for all things sports. This would be all coaching communication, all registration, and payment.
Not all sports are participating in this beta test but I have signed swimming up.
If we participate the company will give our team $500.

All parents should have received an email from a company called Aktive this company has bought registermyathlete and this is who the app is for.
If you can help please go find the email and get the app to help out.

Good morning Team this is Coach Gilbert, we are excited to launch this new App called Aktivate. This new APP along with RMA will allow better communication regarding upcoming workouts, events and any other important information. Every Monday and Friday I will be sending information on upcoming wrestling summer workouts. All athletes must have a 2022/2023 physicals. Tolleson Union HS District announce two location that you can get a physical.

Location: West Point High School
Date: May 19, 2022 (Thursday)
Time: 4pm to 7pm
Appt sign ups will be sent out shortly

Date: May 21, 2022 ( Saturday)
Time: 9am to 12n
Appt sign ups will be sent out shortly.

Thank you,
Coach Gilbert
